title: Death toll from Algerian quake tops 1,000
author: Unknown
text: Residents seach for survivors yesterday in Boumerdes, Algeria, the town hit hardest by Wednesday's earthquake. The toll stands at 1,092  dead. Caption:  photoPhilippe Desmazes / AFP / Getty Images : Residents seach for survivors yesterday in Boumerdes, Algeria, the town hit hardest by Wednesday's earthquake. The toll stands at 1,092 dead. Story, A 2 (0393146422)
